  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give education &amp; sports to 728 children in Bogota</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give the opportunity to 728 children to have a brighter future in Ciudad Bolivar, one of the poorest localities in Bogota, Colombia. We are looking to strengthen the program Goals for a Better Life, which has been developing School tutoring, recreational and sport activities, such as soccer, rugby, basketball, music, Etc. All with the purpose of improve the children quality life by providing an space for personal growth and showing them that they have opportunities to be happy and successful.</narrative>
  </description>
